{"tid":1093482,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"（獌狗射空炮）多蒙特拒賣辛祖","createTime":"2019-04-05T15:18:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T16:13:25.000Z","uid":204475,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a06e087e2a73afc8bc956d7544e7b1414d4a4ded","tid":1093482,"uid":204475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T15:18:51.000Z","msg":"近來有消息稱曼聯有意引進多特小將桑喬。<br />\n<br />\n而多特CEO瓦茨克在接受天空體育採訪時表示：&ldquo;<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">球隊不會賣掉桑喬，這是人盡皆知的事情，他下賽季仍會為多特效力。&rdquo;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n本賽季桑喬取得了巨大的進步，他不僅成為了多特的首發球員，並且幫助多特排在聯賽積分榜榜首的位置。<br />\n<br />\n桑喬本賽季送出了德甲最高的13次助攻，並且進入了英格蘭成年隊。對桑喬的進步，對此瓦茨克表示：&ldquo;桑喬的進步非常大，他的表現也非常出色，但他目前還非常年輕，只有19歲，所以我們不能過度的讚揚他，球隊需要他在比賽時保持專注。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;C羅能一直保持如此高的競技水平並不只是因為他的天賦，更是因為他對比賽有著無與倫比的專注。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;如果桑喬能在未來幾年依舊維持本賽季的狀態，在那我是我們再稱他為世界最佳也不遲。我認為目前我們只能說他是一名有巨大潛力的年輕球員。 &rdquo;"},{"pid":"3aed2520997c37826b4fdcd94948b2381cca52de","tid":1093482,"uid":33730,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T15:21:12.000Z","msg":"首發球員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n躝啦大陸狗"},{"pid":"175f8140b067e5e5a02070af88e1e539ff42075d","tid":1093482,"uid":203961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T15:39:40.000Z","msg":"桑喬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似大陸人講thank you"},{"pid":"3db17e1b47a6ce53e2b1d6fd49aae96841da0290","tid":1093482,"uid":13275,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T15:40:43.000Z","msg":"食屎啦<br />\n有我地偉大既曼聯唔黎留係德甲垃圾聯賽做2弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7277f20905d99e77162f0c93319b674d2b6dcfe7","tid":1093482,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T15:40:43.000Z","msg":"C羅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0cec2ba6b14d465f18ca718dce93de0d8bc676","tid":1093482,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T15:42:05.000Z","msg":"億五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26584d30350c50581f3633fac6fb6ae5f32e9b93","tid":1093482,"uid":186071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T16:13:25.000Z","msg":"兩億啦"}]}